title: Leading Courses - Golf courses

creator: Leadingcourses.com
descriptionHtml:
Secure your next round of golf with the help of thousands of reviews from fellow golfers! Book your tee times directly from the app at thousands of golf courses worldwide. Get inspired by articles written by our content team and ambassadors. Read and filter through 350.000+ trusted reviews of golf clubs and courses written by other golfers, browse through their photos and check green fee rates, the club’s location, the amenities and other helpful golf club and golf course information. Our helpful map will show all the golf clubs nearby and will help you easily navigate to the golf club of your choice!

Join our ever-growing community consisting of more than 150.000 active golfers. Download our app now and become a golf insider immediately!

--------------------------------------------------

All our features are FREE (there is no paid version of the app):

Discover Courses - Use over 350.000+ course ratings and reviews from other golfers to find the best golf courses
View Course Photos - Use 300.000 photos uploaded by our community and course managers to help you decide where to play
Check Relevant Club Info: Read all the relevant information about the club, the rates, the architect, the available amenities and much more
Golf Courses Near You - Find golf courses based on your current location
Book Tee Times - Check where you can play and book tee times in real time and directly into the tee sheets of golf courses
Use Useful Maps - Use our map view and the handy filters to find golf courses that suit your needs
Get Inspired - Read our inspirational blog articles about the best golf courses, the best golf regions and the hidden gems!
Share Your Knowledge - Write reviews, upload your best photos and help our community to grow even further
Build Your Bucket List - Add golf courses to your bucket list
Store Your Memories - By sharing reviews and photos of the golf courses you played you build your own golf logbook, we'll store everything safely for you!
descriptionShort: Leading Courses is golf’s only global community-driven booking portal

Image gallery can now be used for review images
